column3:
Soil: {{soil|soil_type}}

Fertilizer: {{f|f|soil_nitrogen|soil_nitrogen_rate}}

Insects: {{i|i|soil_soil_insects|insect_count}}

Weeds: {{weeds|soil_weed_insects|weed_count}}

Diseases: {{d|d|diseases|diseases_in_soil}}

Fertilizer rates: {{f|f|soil_soil_fertility|fertility_rate}}

{{i|i|soil_soil_insects|insect_count}}

Diseases: {{d|d|diseases|diseases_in_soil}}

Fertilizer rates: {{f|f|soil_soil_fertility|fertility_rate}}

Crop management practices: {{c|c|soil_crops|crops_in_soil}}

```
<p>{% raw %}
<textarea id="soil" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Enter soil type" required>
<input type="hidden" id="soil_type" value="{{d.soil|lower}}" placeholder="Soil type">
</textarea>

<textarea id="soil_nitrogen" class="form-control" rows="10" cols="100%" placeholder="Enter nitrogen level (%)">
<input type="hidden" id="soil_nitrogen_rate" value="{{d.soil_nitrogen|lower}}" placeholder="Soil nitrogen rate">
</textarea>

<textarea id="soil_soil_insects" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Enter soil insects (e.g., 'cocooning' for cocooning web worms)">
<input type="text" id="soil_insect_count" placeholder="Soil insects (cocooning)">
</textarea>

<textarea id="soil_weed_insects" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Enter soil weed insects">
<input type="text" id="soil_weed_insect_count" placeholder="Soil weed insects (cocooning)">
</textarea>

<textarea id="soil_diseases" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Enter soil diseases">
<input type="text" id="soil_disease_count" placeholder="Soil disease (e.g., 'rice blast disease' for brown spot)">
</textarea>

<textarea id="soil_diseases_in_soil" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Enter soil disease in soil">
<input type="text" id="soil_disease_in_soil_count" placeholder="Soil disease in soil (e.g., 'brown spot')">
</textarea>

<textarea id="soil_disease_in_soil" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Enter disease in soil">
<input type="text" id="disease_in_soil_count" placeholder="Disease in soil">
</textarea>

{% for i in d.insect_count %}
<textarea id="f_{{i}}" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Soil insect ({{i|lower}}): " . str(d.soil_insects|lower)){% if i==0 %}
    data-placeholder="Enter soil type"
%}{% if i>0 %}{{i|lower}}:
{% endif %}{% if i==0 %}
<textarea id="{{d.f_insects|lower}}" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Soil insect ({{d.f_insects|lower}}): " . str(d.f_soil_fertility|lower)){% endif %}
    data-placeholder="Enter soil fertility"
{% endif %}
{% if i!=0 %}
    {% for d in data %}
        {% for s in d.soil_insects|list %}
            <input type="hidden" id="{{d.d_insects|lower}}" placeholder="{{s|lower}}">
        {% endfor %}
        {% if i!=0 %}
            {% if i==0 %}
                <input type="hidden" id="{{d.f_soil_fertility|lower}}" placeholder="Fertilizer (soil type ({{d.f_soil_fertility|lower}|lower)): ">
            {% endif %}
            {% for s in d.soil_soil_fertility|list %}
                <input type="hidden" id="{{s|lower}}" placeholder="Soil fertility (e.g., 'soil type')">
            {% endif %}
        {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    {% if i==0 %}
        <textarea id="{{d.soil_soil_fertility|lower}}" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Soil fertility (e.g., 'soil type')">
            {% if i==0 %}
                <input type="hidden" id="{{d.f_soil_fertility|lower}}" placeholder="Soil fertility (e.g., 'soil type')">
            {% else %}
                <input type="hidden" id="{{d.f_soil_fertility|lower}}" placeholder="Fertilizer (soil type ({{d.f_soil_fertility|lower}|lower)): ">
            {% endif %}
        </textarea>
    {% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% if i>0 %}
    <textarea id="{{i.s|lower}}" class="form-control" rows="20" cols="100%" placeholder="Soil insect ({{i.s|lower}}): " . str(i.s|lower)){% endif %}
{% endif %}
{% if i!=0 %}
    <input type="hidden" id="{{d.insects|lower}}" placeholder="Enter insect in soil">
{% endif %}

{% if i==0 %}
    <input type="hidden" id="{{data|lower}}" placeholder="Enter soil type">
{% endif %}
```

Note that I've added the `data-placeholder="Enter soil type"` attribute to the `textarea` elements to ensure that the hidden inputs have a default value. Also, I've used `i.s` instead of `d.soil_soil_fertility` to access the `insects` array.

